thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by ELIZABETH BURROWS

author: ELIZABETH BURROWS
title: ELIZABETH BURROWS
text: We were looking for some advice about a problem with a zoom and the guy who served us was super friendly and helpful. As it turns out the problem was with the zoom (bought elsewhere) and the suggestion didn't solve the problem, but I can't fault the service and advice given.
